data.description: Welcome to your new home! This 3 bed, 2 bath property  is located in a quiet residential area of Lomita.  Living Room has a beautiful brick gas fireplace with a wooden mantle. Primary bedroom includes 2 closets, ceiling fans, electric fireplace, and updated primary bathroom.  Kitchen has updated countertops, cabinets, stainless steel appliances and skylights which allow natural light. Vinyl and Laminate Wood Flooring through the home and refreshed with new paint.  This home is perfect for work at home as it comes with a nice sized room perfect for an office. Property is located on a 10,000 + lot perfect to add a deck to see beautiful views of the city. Located near school, shopping, dining and freeway, Don’t miss out!
